{"tid":2507470,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Uiux designer轉入aco 會否不智?","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T14:33:12.000Z","uid":165758,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e211a7a543511e15c9597a1377ed8e013dac90","tid":2507470,"uid":165758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"小弟本身4-5 年經驗uiux designer, 最近收到aco offer, 好糾結想問下大定意見<br />\n我諗過以下pros and cons.<br />\n<br />\n入:<br />\n- 穩定過世, 頂薪計埋通漲約40k, 冇中年裁員危機, 一直搵到退休<br />\n- 一開始減薪約10k, even more<br />\n- 放棄以後嘅可能性, 冇機會去外國做野 / 生活<br />\n- 個人會越黎越蠢, 簽賣身契<br />\n<br />\n唔入<br />\n- 依加人好過aco, 約25k, 減10k真係好肉痛<br />\n- uiux依行以後重有機會發展, 有機會去外國<br />\n- 搵工唔易, it行業唔敢講自己40歲重有冇人請, 或者多年後會唔會又黎一次肺炎, 比人炒過有陰影, 到時直接去做保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 唔敢講自己做唔做到manager, 最終有冇ACO頂薪個人工<br />\n<br />\n天人交戰, 想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad615a53b80439b8b21d72dd04366faffbf57aa3","tid":2507470,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"想做人定做扯線公仔?"},{"pid":"e623e694e97e0940ae7c9c75b15cc99844a58368","tid":2507470,"uid":45785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"本身幾歲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c7a153f2c3d0ac79c26f9e62919bf4086a95a4","tid":2507470,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"轉羅  <br />\n轉做aco咁都諗得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97403e16f627c61894965fde21d7467324aac45","tid":2507470,"uid":166262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bce81f9eeeb27c7c270dfad66887cadb7ebd438","tid":2507470,"uid":66905,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28